er 2: Corrupted Vision</span><hr size=1>  The trip to the spires was short enough. A smelly gnome wizard offered to take him to the Toxxula forest . . . for a small fee of course. Minz crinkled his nose, hoping the gnome would use the platinum coins to purchase a bath.<br>
