<br>
The &quot;clickity clack&quot; of bones confirmed to him that he was indeed in Paineel. 'Here goes,' he thought. Inwardly readying himself for combat. It was a very real possibility that these guards might not look on him to kindly. Let alone a citizen of Paineel. He snarled at the skeletons, walking toward them as if he'd done it a million times before.<br>
<br>
